WEBVTT

00:00:09.363 --> 00:00:14.428
(This program is intended for mature audiences.
It may feature explicit content, violence, and strong language)

00:00:14.428 --> 00:00:20.396
(All characters, places, and events
in this series are entirely fictitious)

00:00:22.202 --> 00:00:22.785
Well...

00:00:24.935 --> 00:00:26.337
I love you so much.

00:00:27.812 --> 00:00:29.998
But I don't want us to go back
to where we were.

00:00:32.147 --> 00:00:33.932
And if one day we break up again,

00:00:35.335 --> 00:00:37.193
I'll hurt even more than before.

00:00:40.326 --> 00:00:41.546
We're not breaking up again.

00:00:42.803 --> 00:00:44.242
I won't break up with you again, Wayu.

00:00:46.719 --> 00:00:48.740
Well, I just need a little time.

00:00:54.605 --> 00:00:55.625
That's fine.

00:01:00.543 --> 00:01:02.802
Hey, you're just overthinking it.

00:01:03.804 --> 00:01:06.973
Try listening to
your own heart for once.

00:01:08.685 --> 00:01:11.308
Love is never perfect, you know.

00:01:11.490 --> 00:01:13.712
It's all about courage, man.

00:01:14.349 --> 00:01:15.406
The courage to love.

00:01:15.697 --> 00:01:17.610
Just love the way you really want to.

00:01:30.633 --> 00:01:31.343
Yes.

00:01:32.819 --> 00:01:34.075
I'm scared.

00:01:35.423 --> 00:01:37.500
I'm just... I'm scared of everything.

00:01:38.392 --> 00:01:40.742
All these problems
still aren't sorted out.

00:01:41.252 --> 00:01:43.656
He's got a fiancée
he's supposed to marry.

00:01:45.496 --> 00:01:47.153
And then there's his dad too.

00:01:47.590 --> 00:01:50.268
So what happens if I keep seeing him?

00:01:52.326 --> 00:01:54.293
In the end,
we'll still have to break up.

00:01:57.699 --> 00:01:59.320
This part is on you, man.

00:02:00.067 --> 00:02:02.963
Do you actually want to work
through it all with him?

00:02:08.628 --> 00:02:11.706
If you really love him,
and are ready to face everything,

00:02:12.015 --> 00:02:13.418
just go for it.

00:02:14.237 --> 00:02:16.733
But if you're scared of getting hurt,
then don't.

00:02:17.753 --> 00:02:19.520
That's your answer, right?

00:02:19.702 --> 00:02:21.432
That you're just not ready to move on.

00:02:23.654 --> 00:02:25.184
But let me just say this.

00:02:26.077 --> 00:02:29.920
A second chance isn't something
everyone always gets, you know.

00:02:37.060 --> 00:02:38.262
More.

00:03:29.462 --> 00:03:33.105
Alright, guys, turn in
your work next week.

00:03:33.105 --> 00:03:34.288
See you!

00:03:34.744 --> 00:03:37.494
- Goodbye, ma'am.
- Goodbye.

00:03:38.915 --> 00:03:40.591
Don't drink too late at night.

00:03:45.690 --> 00:03:46.947
Go ahead and eat.

00:03:53.887 --> 00:03:55.417
No.

00:04:05.016 --> 00:04:06.240
(Tai Moonlit)
(We've got an event tonight.)

00:04:06.240 --> 00:04:07.912
(Come help at the bar.)

00:04:31.718 --> 00:04:32.628
Foei.

00:04:41.735 --> 00:04:44.959
(I'm someone who's too scared
to come out and say)

00:04:45.160 --> 00:04:46.544
(what my sexual orientation is.)

00:04:48.329 --> 00:04:51.352
(I'm the only son,
the family's big hope.)

00:04:52.409 --> 00:04:54.977
(But after I had
a near-death experience,)

00:04:56.270 --> 00:04:59.057
(today I want to
follow my heart for once.)

00:05:01.297 --> 00:05:03.683
(I only posted this picture
in a burner account.)

00:05:04.284 --> 00:05:05.505
(But now)

00:05:05.723 --> 00:05:07.526
(I want to show it to the whole world)

00:05:07.873 --> 00:05:10.295
(that this is the person I love.)

00:05:19.074 --> 00:05:23.610
♪My heart is waiting for you to take it♪

00:05:23.628 --> 00:05:29.893
♪My heart is filled with nothing
but love for you, can you hear it?♪

00:05:29.893 --> 00:05:36.815
♪And I won't look at anyone else,
I won't want anyone else♪

00:05:37.562 --> 00:05:43.445
♪Please accept this love
from someone so ordinary♪

00:05:43.973 --> 00:05:48.290
♪Let me be the one to take you
drifting far, far away♪

00:05:48.435 --> 00:05:53.025
♪All the way to the horizon,
where the stars are shining♪

00:05:53.025 --> 00:05:57.014
♪Will you be the one
to make our love sweet?♪

00:05:57.014 --> 00:06:01.659
♪Please give your heart
to this ordinary guy♪

00:06:02.005 --> 00:06:06.376
♪You helped me see♪

00:06:06.376 --> 00:06:11.440
♪That someone like me
can truly mean something♪

00:06:11.731 --> 00:06:17.814
♪All because of your love,
your heart for me♪

00:06:23.661 --> 00:06:24.536
Wayu.

00:06:29.035 --> 00:06:31.803
I don't care anymore what my dad

00:06:32.149 --> 00:06:34.007
or anyone in this world says.

00:06:34.553 --> 00:06:36.011
Or how they see me.

00:06:37.085 --> 00:06:38.834
Right now, I only care about you, Wayu.

00:06:42.841 --> 00:06:44.061
And I promise,

00:06:45.209 --> 00:06:46.921
I won't hurt you again, Wayu.

00:06:47.686 --> 00:06:52.513
♪To truly understand
a love beyond reason♪

00:06:52.513 --> 00:06:57.103
♪When I found someone like you♪

00:06:57.103 --> 00:07:01.784
♪My whole life no longer
has to keep dreaming♪

00:07:02.130 --> 00:07:05.936
♪Now that you're right here♪

00:07:06.009 --> 00:07:07.649
Make sure you keep your word.

00:07:08.468 --> 00:07:13.149
♪I love you with all my heart,
and I'm ready to give you everything♪

00:07:13.149 --> 00:07:18.194
♪All one life can offer♪

00:07:18.267 --> 00:07:23.259
♪I won't leave you behind,
no matter what I face♪

00:07:23.259 --> 00:07:26.606
♪No matter how bad♪

00:07:26.609 --> 00:07:31.327
♪I give you my all,
my body and everything♪

00:07:31.327 --> 00:07:36.172
♪Please trust your life
with someone like me♪

00:07:36.172 --> 00:07:42.144
Wow.

00:07:42.272 --> 00:07:47.099
- Wow, that's extremely sweet!
- How is it so sweet?

00:07:47.537 --> 00:07:49.996
Right in the middle of my bar!

00:07:49.996 --> 00:07:52.237
That's nothing.

00:07:56.025 --> 00:07:59.468
Aww!

00:07:59.468 --> 00:08:04.313
Look at him swallowing
state property. Ouch!

00:08:04.313 --> 00:08:07.445
Get a room, you two! I'll pay for it!

00:08:07.445 --> 00:08:08.720
Tai, don't cry, Tai.

00:08:08.811 --> 00:08:13.529
♪No one could ever
love you more than I do♪

00:08:13.529 --> 00:08:20.195
♪No one could ever
love you more than I do♪

00:08:20.195 --> 00:08:24.949
=Love of Silom=

00:08:40.759 --> 00:08:42.253
The necklace has returned
to its owner, huh?

00:08:46.223 --> 00:08:46.915
Hey.

00:08:47.935 --> 00:08:49.174
I won't let you take it off anymore.

00:08:54.329 --> 00:08:55.767
Then behave yourself, okay?

00:08:56.569 --> 00:08:59.592
If nothing happens, I won't take it off.

00:09:00.266 --> 00:09:01.050
Ouch.

00:09:03.308 --> 00:09:04.565
Touched a nerve.

00:09:11.304 --> 00:09:12.707
Thanks for bringing it back.

00:09:23.599 --> 00:09:24.509
What are you doing?

00:09:25.311 --> 00:09:26.568
It's a contest.

00:09:27.150 --> 00:09:30.411
My professor recommended entering,
so I just went for it.

00:09:30.611 --> 00:09:32.287
Not sure if I'll win anything, though.

00:09:33.981 --> 00:09:34.910
Sigh.

00:09:35.602 --> 00:09:38.826
There's so much to do,
plus my final project.

00:09:42.177 --> 00:09:43.579
You can do it.

00:09:44.982 --> 00:09:46.239
Anything you want me to help with?

00:09:51.740 --> 00:09:52.778
There will be.

00:09:55.145 --> 00:09:56.694
I've got a secret file too.

00:09:59.480 --> 00:10:00.555
Are you trying to tease me?

00:10:02.103 --> 00:10:05.145
Not like that, you dirty mind.

00:10:06.074 --> 00:10:07.276
Look at this.

00:10:08.697 --> 00:10:11.301
I also designed a version of our house.

00:10:12.267 --> 00:10:13.578
Do you see this part here?

00:10:13.578 --> 00:10:15.290
There's space here, too.

00:10:15.290 --> 00:10:17.640
It's for Singto to run around
and for other things.

00:10:17.640 --> 00:10:21.082
Our family can come here to camp.

00:10:21.082 --> 00:10:21.975
Like it?

00:10:22.758 --> 00:10:23.669
I like it.

00:10:24.488 --> 00:10:27.312
Honestly, I like all of it.

00:10:27.603 --> 00:10:28.732
It's really up to you, Wayu.

00:10:30.226 --> 00:10:31.792
I'm just here to pay.

00:10:32.521 --> 00:10:35.654
Oh, come on.

00:10:46.691 --> 00:10:47.456
Yes, Dad.

00:10:47.456 --> 00:10:51.190
- Get to HQ right now.
- Got it. I'll hurry over.

00:10:52.830 --> 00:10:54.432
Hey, Krit!

00:10:55.452 --> 00:10:56.582
Something wrong?

00:10:58.603 --> 00:11:01.463
No, I just got called in urgently.

00:11:02.920 --> 00:11:04.177
Is it about me?

00:11:04.578 --> 00:11:05.762
Want me to come with you?

00:11:06.581 --> 00:11:08.202
I can handle this.

00:11:09.514 --> 00:11:12.027
Don't worry. I'll be back soon.

00:11:18.457 --> 00:11:20.357
Hmm, okay.

00:11:32.828 --> 00:11:34.248
What is wrong with you?

00:11:34.886 --> 00:11:37.764
You paraded that kid around,
so how am I supposed to show my face?

00:11:38.419 --> 00:11:40.387
You're supposed to marry Mint.

00:11:40.660 --> 00:11:42.135
What were you thinking?

00:11:43.956 --> 00:11:47.545
The minister was never going to let you
marry his daughter.

00:11:48.219 --> 00:11:49.931
Go delete that post.

00:11:50.259 --> 00:11:52.645
Then go apologize
to the minister with me.

00:11:52.809 --> 00:11:53.555
No.

00:11:55.923 --> 00:11:57.799
I won't marry anyone.

00:11:58.236 --> 00:11:59.384
Except Wayu.

00:12:01.132 --> 00:12:02.316
No, you can't.

00:12:03.500 --> 00:12:05.249
You can't marry him.

00:12:07.161 --> 00:12:08.801
I'm transferring you upcountry.

00:12:09.256 --> 00:12:10.841
Go do desk work.

00:12:11.351 --> 00:12:12.862
No more fieldwork.

00:12:13.026 --> 00:12:15.777
- It's for your own safety.
- Dad...

00:12:18.327 --> 00:12:21.131
Police risk their lives
to protect people, right?

00:12:25.084 --> 00:12:26.304
And as your son,

00:12:27.288 --> 00:12:29.710
I have the right to love whoever I want.

00:12:31.623 --> 00:12:34.464
Please give orders without dragging
personal matters into it.

00:12:40.712 --> 00:12:41.877
If that's all,

00:12:42.460 --> 00:12:43.717
I'll excuse myself.

00:12:57.614 --> 00:12:59.818
I don't know what's so great
about that kid

00:12:59.818 --> 00:13:01.585
for Krit to be that crazy about him.

00:13:01.749 --> 00:13:03.497
There are lots of good women out there.

00:13:04.135 --> 00:13:06.721
Do you know
everyone's talking about it now?

00:13:07.049 --> 00:13:11.038
The minister even called me
to cancel the wedding plans.

00:13:11.257 --> 00:13:13.224
I don't even know where to put my face.

00:13:13.497 --> 00:13:15.464
It's the most embarrassing thing.

00:13:18.287 --> 00:13:19.708
There's nothing to be embarrassed about

00:13:20.692 --> 00:13:22.203
if it's what makes our child happy.

00:13:23.151 --> 00:13:24.316
Are you crazy?

00:13:25.009 --> 00:13:27.213
Do you want our child
to go back to that kid?

00:13:27.595 --> 00:13:31.219
This is getting crazy.
What are you thinking?

00:13:33.478 --> 00:13:35.882
And you, what are you thinking?

00:13:36.374 --> 00:13:39.197
When Krit was sick,
lying in the hospital,

00:13:39.270 --> 00:13:42.148
it was only Wayu
who really cared about Krit.

00:13:42.421 --> 00:13:44.534
Even after you drove him away like that.

00:13:44.534 --> 00:13:46.610
He still found ways
to take care of Krit.

00:13:47.266 --> 00:13:50.891
And Mint, did she ever
visit Krit, even once?

00:13:51.528 --> 00:13:54.479
And you still want our child
to marry someone like that?

00:13:55.754 --> 00:13:59.578
Anyone but a man, I can't accept it.

00:14:02.202 --> 00:14:04.733
Times have changed.
It's not like our era anymore.

00:14:04.988 --> 00:14:06.737
I want you to open your heart a little.

00:14:07.302 --> 00:14:09.834
What's wrong with Krit and Wayu?

00:14:10.471 --> 00:14:12.074
They're just in love.

00:14:12.638 --> 00:14:14.332
It's just like you and me.

00:14:15.152 --> 00:14:16.864
It's just that they're the same gender.

00:14:17.497 --> 00:14:20.407
You can't devalue
our child's love like that.

00:14:20.871 --> 00:14:22.401
I'm not devaluing it.

00:14:23.111 --> 00:14:24.860
But it's not appropriate.

00:14:24.860 --> 00:14:26.335
How is it not appropriate?

00:14:26.863 --> 00:14:30.014
Does it have to be a man and a woman
for them to be in love?

00:14:31.107 --> 00:14:32.637
Let me ask you one thing.

00:14:32.892 --> 00:14:35.060
If one of your subordinates
loved the same gender,

00:14:35.424 --> 00:14:37.482
would you force them to break up?

00:14:38.593 --> 00:14:39.759
Of course not.

00:14:42.054 --> 00:14:44.149
Marriage equality is legal now.

00:14:45.187 --> 00:14:47.500
Society is more accepting of diversity.

00:14:48.465 --> 00:14:51.981
Everyone has freedom
of thought and emotion.

00:14:53.456 --> 00:14:56.370
It's time for you to respect

00:14:56.370 --> 00:14:58.793
and understand our child's decisions.

00:15:01.580 --> 00:15:04.184
I really want to see our child
truly happy for once.

00:15:51.249 --> 00:15:53.016
- Krit.
- Hmm?

00:15:53.854 --> 00:15:55.839
Should I go visit your dad?

00:15:57.060 --> 00:16:00.029
I could go and ask him properly.

00:16:01.340 --> 00:16:04.527
Maybe he'll change his mind.

00:16:09.536 --> 00:16:10.520
It won't work.

00:16:26.457 --> 00:16:28.042
So what should we do?

00:16:30.064 --> 00:16:33.196
I don't want you
to get transferred out of town.

00:16:36.275 --> 00:16:37.732
I don't want to go either.

00:16:39.389 --> 00:16:40.282
It's okay.

00:16:40.755 --> 00:16:42.996
Let's wait until my dad
calms down a bit first.

00:16:43.560 --> 00:16:45.109
Then I'll try talking to him.

00:16:47.422 --> 00:16:48.205
Okay.

00:16:56.183 --> 00:16:58.223
If anything happens,
you have to tell me.

00:16:59.935 --> 00:17:01.683
It's not just about you.

00:17:02.740 --> 00:17:05.363
It's about both of us, you know.

00:17:16.710 --> 00:17:17.420
Yeah.

00:17:18.495 --> 00:17:19.369
Hmm.

00:17:21.846 --> 00:17:22.830
Then...

00:17:25.526 --> 00:17:27.402
Then let's do something just for us.

00:17:32.392 --> 00:17:35.871
- Ouch!
- Hey! Wait till you're better.

00:17:37.784 --> 00:17:39.387
Then we can do stuff together.

00:17:41.900 --> 00:17:43.558
It's a lot better now.

00:17:45.962 --> 00:17:46.873
It's really fine.

00:17:49.131 --> 00:17:49.987
I can still do it.

00:17:51.062 --> 00:17:53.393
Mm... Hey.

00:17:53.812 --> 00:17:55.797
No. Absolutely not.

00:17:55.797 --> 00:17:58.238
If you're being stubborn
and won't stay in the hospital,

00:17:58.238 --> 00:18:00.442
then you need to fully recover first.

00:18:00.442 --> 00:18:02.482
Forget it. Blow-dry my hair, now.

00:18:02.482 --> 00:18:06.143
- I'm fine now.
- No, you're not. Don't, Krit.

00:18:06.143 --> 00:18:07.327
Blow-dry my hair first.

00:18:08.292 --> 00:18:11.425
Just wait till you're better. Hurry.
My hair's not even dry yet. Ouch!

00:18:12.737 --> 00:18:14.959
- Krit.
- Hey.

00:18:15.451 --> 00:18:17.090
Come on, blow-dry my hair first. Hurry.

00:18:21.097 --> 00:18:22.919
Mom, what are we eating today?

00:18:29.421 --> 00:18:30.641
Mom, how did you get here?

00:18:33.082 --> 00:18:34.193
What are you doing here, anyway?

00:18:34.867 --> 00:18:36.451
I came to see you, of course.

00:18:36.870 --> 00:18:38.983
Do you ever plan on coming home?

00:18:38.983 --> 00:18:41.237
Let your mom see your face
once in a while, huh?

00:18:43.154 --> 00:18:44.910
But you shouldn't just show up
like this, Mom.

00:18:44.910 --> 00:18:46.910
At least call me first.

00:18:47.526 --> 00:18:50.749
Why don't we all stay
and have breakfast here?

00:18:52.316 --> 00:18:53.900
- Please, go ahead.
- Please.

00:18:54.993 --> 00:18:56.159
Krit, have a seat.

00:18:56.159 --> 00:18:58.272
- Sorry for the trouble.
- It's okay.

00:19:02.661 --> 00:19:03.518
Here.

00:19:05.885 --> 00:19:07.160
Thank you.

00:19:07.925 --> 00:19:11.186
Then I'll feed Singto first.
It's about time.

00:19:12.206 --> 00:19:13.590
Here you go, Singto.

00:19:14.227 --> 00:19:15.685
Come on, have some rice.

00:19:16.450 --> 00:19:17.123
Come on.

00:19:18.927 --> 00:19:22.934
Ah... Oops, what was that?

00:19:23.553 --> 00:19:25.447
Ah. Is that okay?

00:19:25.447 --> 00:19:28.052
Ah, good job.

00:19:28.271 --> 00:19:30.110
- Dad, eat.
- Dad, eat.

00:19:30.110 --> 00:19:32.587
Ah. Mmm.

00:19:32.587 --> 00:19:34.645
Hmm? Can you feed Papa?

00:19:35.247 --> 00:19:38.725
- Ah, good job.
- So tasty.

00:19:38.725 --> 00:19:40.620
It'd be nice
if Krit had a child of his own.

00:19:41.403 --> 00:19:42.314
Mom.

00:19:43.352 --> 00:19:47.341
If you don't, that's okay.
I'm not complaining.

00:19:47.760 --> 00:19:50.528
Actually, the reason I came today

00:19:50.820 --> 00:19:53.606
is that I wanted to get to know
Wayu's family.

00:19:56.047 --> 00:19:58.269
You two have been together
for a while now.

00:19:58.706 --> 00:20:02.367
Krit, you still haven't officially
introduced me to Wayu's family.

00:20:04.517 --> 00:20:05.409
Wayu.

00:20:06.320 --> 00:20:08.469
- Yes.
- Thank you so much

00:20:08.724 --> 00:20:11.037
for taking care of Krit
while he was in the hospital.

00:20:11.893 --> 00:20:14.006
Oh, really, there's no need to thank me.

00:20:14.006 --> 00:20:16.447
It's just something
I'm supposed to do anyway.

00:20:17.011 --> 00:20:20.144
Actually, Krit doesn't even
need to have kids.

00:20:20.672 --> 00:20:23.368
I've got one I can donate, ready to go.

00:20:24.844 --> 00:20:27.120
Right? Isn't that right?

00:20:27.120 --> 00:20:30.745
- Hey!
- Not sharing with your mom?

00:20:30.872 --> 00:20:33.860
So good.

00:20:33.860 --> 00:20:35.462
Hey.

00:20:35.462 --> 00:20:37.976
That's enough. Give it here.

00:20:40.289 --> 00:20:43.021
About Dad, don't worry.

00:20:43.495 --> 00:20:45.353
I'll talk to him myself.

00:20:49.906 --> 00:20:51.054
Won't you end up arguing?

00:20:53.531 --> 00:20:56.591
If we have to argue, I'm ready.

00:20:57.720 --> 00:21:00.106
I really want to see you
happy for once, Krit.

00:21:01.254 --> 00:21:02.966
All this time,

00:21:03.457 --> 00:21:05.607
you've always done everything
for the family.

00:21:06.536 --> 00:21:07.537
But this time,

00:21:07.920 --> 00:21:10.597
I want you to follow
your own heart, Krit.

00:21:18.593 --> 00:21:19.522
Thank you.

00:21:30.869 --> 00:21:32.016
I love you.

00:21:32.727 --> 00:21:33.638
I love you too.

00:21:46.133 --> 00:21:47.226
Hey, what's going on?

00:21:47.900 --> 00:21:49.193
Wayu, you haven't seen it?

00:21:49.193 --> 00:21:52.034
The hall you designed got picked
to move forward.

00:21:52.581 --> 00:21:55.003
- Really?
- Yeah. Look.

00:21:59.684 --> 00:22:02.089
Congrats, man. Congrats.

00:22:02.089 --> 00:22:04.566
I can't wait to see your project.

00:22:04.566 --> 00:22:06.187
- I'm happy for you.
- You're the best.

00:22:06.806 --> 00:22:08.190
So when do we get to see your building?

00:22:08.192 --> 00:22:10.885
(Congratulations to
Sipakorn Tangsamai, Winner)

00:22:10.904 --> 00:22:14.019
This is the hall
we'll be completely renovating.

00:22:14.019 --> 00:22:16.150
I'll be counting on both of you.

00:22:16.332 --> 00:22:17.826
Of course, we'd be happy to.

00:22:17.898 --> 00:22:19.047
- Yes.
- Thank you.

00:22:19.047 --> 00:22:22.033
So, do you think
we can finish it in time?

00:22:22.033 --> 00:22:23.909
Oh, I'm sure we'll make it.

00:22:23.909 --> 00:22:25.822
Because honestly, it's just...

00:22:26.769 --> 00:22:29.155
It's really not that different,
at least in my opinion...

00:22:29.155 --> 00:22:30.667
Hello, Mr. Pitak.

00:22:30.885 --> 00:22:31.814
Hello.

00:22:32.087 --> 00:22:33.799
You're here for the seminar today, sir?

00:22:33.799 --> 00:22:35.056
Oh, yes.

00:22:38.517 --> 00:22:41.340
Oh, this is the interior designer
who won the contest.

00:22:41.468 --> 00:22:43.781
He'll be handling
the full renovation of this hall.

00:22:44.746 --> 00:22:47.569
And this is the engineer
who's overseeing the project.

00:22:48.444 --> 00:22:49.409
- Hello.
- Hello.

00:22:50.520 --> 00:22:52.760
If you'll excuse me, sir,
I'll take my leave now.

00:22:52.760 --> 00:22:54.873
- All right.
- Goodbye, please go ahead.

00:22:57.059 --> 00:23:00.228
This designer is talented,
and he's good-looking too.

00:23:00.847 --> 00:23:03.197
Yeah. I heard he hasn't even finished
his fourth year yet.

00:23:03.197 --> 00:23:04.927
But he's good at design.

00:23:05.364 --> 00:23:06.913
With talent like this, he'll go far.

00:23:16.184 --> 00:23:19.244
Welcome back, Captain.

00:23:21.702 --> 00:23:24.070
Thank you, everyone. Carry on.

00:23:24.890 --> 00:23:27.203
How are you?
You're all better now, Captain?

00:23:28.168 --> 00:23:30.281
Yes, I'm much better now.

00:23:30.773 --> 00:23:33.214
- Just waiting for the wound to heal.
- Mm.

00:23:33.214 --> 00:23:34.143
But I promise that

00:23:34.380 --> 00:23:35.800
it definitely won't affect my work.

00:23:37.057 --> 00:23:40.936
Don't worry.
Make the most of your days off.

00:23:40.936 --> 00:23:42.740
Because once you're back,

00:23:42.813 --> 00:23:45.854
you won't get any sleep at all, Captain.

00:23:46.346 --> 00:23:47.257
Hm, yes.

00:23:47.585 --> 00:23:49.497
Anyway, congratulations.

00:23:50.208 --> 00:23:53.759
- This case was solved thanks to you.
- Yes.

00:23:54.342 --> 00:23:56.965
No, it's because
everyone worked together.

00:23:57.949 --> 00:24:00.571
- Thank you, everyone.
- Yes.

00:24:02.156 --> 00:24:03.140
Captain.

00:24:04.068 --> 00:24:05.052
Carry on.

00:24:06.036 --> 00:24:08.514
I have something to discuss with you.
Come with me to my office.

00:24:21.117 --> 00:24:24.814
- What are you staring at? Get back to work.
- Yes, sir.

00:24:32.446 --> 00:24:33.302
Hmm.

00:24:38.657 --> 00:24:40.023
If you have something to say, sir,
just say it.

00:24:40.515 --> 00:24:41.826
I have work I need to get back to.

00:24:44.212 --> 00:24:46.216
You want to keep working
in this unit, right?

00:24:50.296 --> 00:24:51.116
Yes.

00:24:53.702 --> 00:24:54.831
Then that's settled.

00:24:55.960 --> 00:24:57.472
Do good work.

00:24:58.492 --> 00:25:00.623
So I can recommend you for promotion.

00:25:06.197 --> 00:25:06.998
Sure.

00:25:08.801 --> 00:25:09.548
Wait.

00:25:14.084 --> 00:25:15.031
Hmm.

00:25:16.870 --> 00:25:17.745
When you're free...

00:25:19.566 --> 00:25:21.351
bring your boyfriend over
for dinner at our place.

00:25:23.118 --> 00:25:24.302
So we can get to know him.

00:25:29.748 --> 00:25:30.840
Are you serious, Dad?

00:25:32.134 --> 00:25:33.573
When you're going, call your mom first.

00:25:35.084 --> 00:25:36.596
So she can make extra food.

00:25:43.226 --> 00:25:44.119
Alright.

00:25:46.359 --> 00:25:47.306
Thank you.

00:25:49.073 --> 00:25:49.892
Go.

00:25:54.155 --> 00:25:55.302
Take care.

00:25:57.542 --> 00:26:00.092
That was way too formal?

00:26:02.806 --> 00:26:05.575
Yeah, like a bouncer at Moonlit.

00:26:06.158 --> 00:26:07.743
Hey, you idiot, Tai!

00:26:10.001 --> 00:26:12.514
It's just dinner with your partner's parents!
Do you really need to be...

00:26:12.951 --> 00:26:15.151
this darn serious? Huh?

00:26:16.030 --> 00:26:18.598
It has to be this serious, man.
You know that...

00:26:18.853 --> 00:26:20.529
He doesn't really like the look of me.

00:26:21.039 --> 00:26:22.824
At least, I have to make
a good impression on him.

00:26:22.900 --> 00:26:26.377
So why did the Captain's dad
suddenly invite you to dinner?

00:26:26.831 --> 00:26:28.634
Is he going to scold you or something?

00:26:30.892 --> 00:26:32.914
I don't think so.

00:26:32.969 --> 00:26:35.865
His mom probably talked him into it.

00:26:37.996 --> 00:26:39.271
And if, out of nowhere,

00:26:39.799 --> 00:26:43.843
he offered you ten million
to stop seeing Captain,

00:26:44.972 --> 00:26:46.065
what would you do then?

00:26:49.453 --> 00:26:52.585
I'd probably ask
for twenty million instead.

00:26:52.822 --> 00:26:55.591
I'd get a nice house
and some luxury cars too.

00:26:55.700 --> 00:26:58.578
Then I'll ask for two million
for myself too... Hey!

00:26:58.851 --> 00:27:01.292
That'd be terrible. But seriously...

00:27:01.292 --> 00:27:03.292
If he really said that,
what would you do?

00:27:03.350 --> 00:27:05.099
I wouldn't have to do anything.

00:27:05.099 --> 00:27:06.876
Because I wouldn't take it anyway.

00:27:08.104 --> 00:27:09.436
Because Captain

00:27:09.436 --> 00:27:11.745
is worth more than ten million.

00:27:12.694 --> 00:27:14.879
- Gross.
- Ugh, get out of here.

00:27:14.879 --> 00:27:16.027
I'm sick of all this love stuff.

00:27:16.592 --> 00:27:19.123
Seriously, check this first.
How's this outfit?

00:27:20.089 --> 00:27:24.078
Hmm, I think something more casual
would be better.

00:27:24.606 --> 00:27:28.158
It looks way too much.
Take the suit off. This one is better.

00:27:28.759 --> 00:27:31.418
- Too much?
- Yeah. I think this one.

00:27:33.112 --> 00:27:36.336
See? Looks nice and casual.
Check it out.

00:27:36.591 --> 00:27:38.977
- Your shirt looks super old.
- Hey.

00:27:40.470 --> 00:27:43.330
There you go. You look good.
Nice and casual.

00:27:48.758 --> 00:27:51.672
Open wide, come on. Ah.

00:27:52.291 --> 00:27:56.408
Ah. Oh, Singto.

00:27:56.499 --> 00:27:58.575
It's all over you. What a mess.

00:27:59.194 --> 00:28:00.797
- Krit.
- Yeah.

00:28:05.078 --> 00:28:06.134
Come on. One more time.

00:28:06.899 --> 00:28:09.868
- Feed me.
- Papa will feed you.

00:28:11.380 --> 00:28:13.347
- Ah.
- Sir.

00:28:13.693 --> 00:28:15.496
I'm sorry. It's just that

00:28:15.496 --> 00:28:17.172
there's no one at home.

00:28:17.172 --> 00:28:19.518
My mom and sister
went to a neighbor's funeral.

00:28:19.922 --> 00:28:22.909
I have to bring my nephew along.
I'm sorry.

00:28:23.765 --> 00:28:24.767
- It's okay.
- Okay.

00:28:24.767 --> 00:28:26.807
Kid does brighten things up.

00:28:29.229 --> 00:28:30.942
Hmm.

00:28:31.743 --> 00:28:34.858
By the way, are you
an interior designer?

00:28:35.295 --> 00:28:38.318
Yeah. I'm about to graduate.

00:28:38.883 --> 00:28:41.979
And... What about your other job?

00:28:45.167 --> 00:28:47.571
- A bar host, right?
- Yeah.

00:28:48.081 --> 00:28:50.922
The reason I had to work
as a bar host was that

00:28:50.941 --> 00:28:52.580
I was having money problems.

00:28:52.616 --> 00:28:55.002
I have to support my nephew
and take care of my mom.

00:28:55.458 --> 00:28:57.079
So I started working as a bar host.

00:28:57.079 --> 00:28:59.793
But I've quit now.

00:29:00.175 --> 00:29:02.106
Now I'm focusing on finishing my degree.

00:29:02.561 --> 00:29:04.037
That's good.

00:29:06.022 --> 00:29:06.951
Sir.

00:29:08.226 --> 00:29:09.774
Don't worry.

00:29:09.774 --> 00:29:13.143
I'd never use Krit for his money.
You can trust me.

00:29:13.544 --> 00:29:14.929
Okay. Mm.

00:29:17.060 --> 00:29:18.571
Mouth, messy.

00:29:19.760 --> 00:29:20.613
Hmm?

00:29:20.775 --> 00:29:23.671
- Mouth's messy.
- Mouth's messy.

00:29:24.400 --> 00:29:25.985
- Messy.
- Here you go.

00:29:26.039 --> 00:29:27.679
Help wipe him, okay?

00:29:27.679 --> 00:29:30.119
- Come on.
- Whoa.

00:29:32.523 --> 00:29:34.145
- Good job.
- Good job.

00:29:35.857 --> 00:29:36.786
Come on.

00:29:40.246 --> 00:29:42.195
Let's have dinner now.

00:29:42.195 --> 00:29:43.616
I'll dish it up for you.

00:29:43.616 --> 00:29:46.585
- Go on. Serve her too.
- Thank you.

00:29:49.226 --> 00:29:49.954
Here you go.

00:29:50.610 --> 00:29:53.870
- Oh, wow.
- Thank you very much.

00:29:54.216 --> 00:29:57.204
- Sir, may I?
- Thanks a lot.

00:30:02.923 --> 00:30:04.034
Here, some veggies.

00:30:05.946 --> 00:30:10.609
Hmm.

00:30:10.609 --> 00:30:12.558
Oh, that's such a beautiful watch.

00:30:12.558 --> 00:30:14.671
- Hehe.
- Hmm, huh?

00:30:15.855 --> 00:30:20.550
Okay, let's go home now. Let's go.

00:30:21.264 --> 00:30:22.703
We're heading home now.

00:30:22.958 --> 00:30:25.745
I'll take Wayu and Singto home first.

00:30:25.745 --> 00:30:26.783
- Sure.
- Okay.

00:30:26.783 --> 00:30:29.789
Say goodbye to Grandpa
and Grandma. Goodbye.

00:30:29.789 --> 00:30:31.665
- So cute.
- So, I'll take my leave now.

00:30:31.665 --> 00:30:32.830
- Okay.
- Alright.

00:30:32.830 --> 00:30:34.761
Up we go, up.

00:30:34.761 --> 00:30:37.402
- Grandpa's number first.
- What was that?

00:30:37.402 --> 00:30:39.479
- Grandpa's and Grandma's numbers.
- You ask for Grandpa's number too!

00:30:39.479 --> 00:30:41.555
Grandpa's and Grandma's number?
How do I do that?

00:30:41.555 --> 00:30:42.684
How do you ask for a number?

00:30:42.684 --> 00:30:45.289
- Oh, let me do it.
- Sure.

00:30:45.362 --> 00:30:46.819
- Watch.
- My number first then.

00:30:46.819 --> 00:30:47.584
Okay.

00:30:47.584 --> 00:30:49.259
You want both?

00:30:50.316 --> 00:30:53.285
- Oh, so that's how you do it.
- Mm.

00:30:53.285 --> 00:30:54.815
Thank you.

00:30:55.052 --> 00:30:58.057
- Oh.
- Say thank you. Quick.

00:30:58.130 --> 00:31:00.989
Say thank you first. Thank you. Then...

00:31:01.372 --> 00:31:02.720
We're really leaving now.

00:31:02.720 --> 00:31:05.634
- Okay.
- Goodbye.

00:31:05.634 --> 00:31:06.964
- I'll get going.
- Bye-bye.

00:31:06.964 --> 00:31:08.457
Go.

00:31:08.457 --> 00:31:10.315
- Bye-bye, dear.
- Up.

00:31:11.153 --> 00:31:12.847
- Drive safely, dear.
- Okay.

00:31:26.580 --> 00:31:27.363
Coffee.

00:31:28.474 --> 00:31:29.950
Thank you.

00:31:31.097 --> 00:31:32.427
Lean on this, or your back will hurt.

00:31:39.330 --> 00:31:40.641
Sigh.

00:31:41.898 --> 00:31:43.355
Probably all night long.

00:31:44.885 --> 00:31:47.964
It's okay. I'll stay here with you.

00:31:49.712 --> 00:31:51.515
Don't you have to work tomorrow?

00:31:53.701 --> 00:31:54.539
I do.

00:31:57.180 --> 00:31:58.819
But I want to be with my boyfriend.

00:32:00.968 --> 00:32:04.393
No, it's almost 2 AM.

00:32:04.921 --> 00:32:06.014
You should go to sleep.

00:32:07.944 --> 00:32:09.365
You're not that young anymore.

00:32:09.766 --> 00:32:12.680
Sleeping less will wear your body out.

00:32:17.306 --> 00:32:19.073
Just wait until you get old.

00:32:20.203 --> 00:32:22.661
I'm just teasing. I want you to rest.

00:32:24.155 --> 00:32:26.159
You've just been badly hurt too.

00:32:26.705 --> 00:32:27.761
Go. Go to sleep.

00:32:30.748 --> 00:32:31.677
Okay.

00:32:33.007 --> 00:32:34.592
Go. Go to bed quickly.

00:32:34.737 --> 00:32:36.978
- Okay, I'll go to sleep first.
- Mm.

00:32:37.652 --> 00:32:38.945
And don't overdo it, Wayu.

00:32:41.641 --> 00:32:43.662
- Good night.
- Good night.

00:32:44.846 --> 00:32:45.720
Mm.

00:33:39.306 --> 00:33:40.181
Wayu.

00:33:41.401 --> 00:33:42.293
It's morning.

00:33:43.423 --> 00:33:45.590
Go lie down properly,
or your neck will start hurting.

00:33:46.993 --> 00:33:48.832
Mm.

00:33:53.313 --> 00:33:54.989
Come on. Go sleep in your bed.

00:33:55.663 --> 00:33:56.428
Come here.

00:33:56.974 --> 00:33:58.194
Mm.

00:34:06.773 --> 00:34:07.629
Let's go.

00:34:28.794 --> 00:34:29.687
Krit.

00:34:32.273 --> 00:34:36.408
Yay, I've graduated!

00:34:38.794 --> 00:34:39.905
Well done.

00:34:40.979 --> 00:34:41.890
I'm happy for you.

00:34:42.382 --> 00:34:43.902
Come on, let's celebrate today.

00:34:43.966 --> 00:34:45.460
Sure! Where should we go?

00:35:00.596 --> 00:35:03.255
I thought you'd take me
somewhere special.

00:35:05.751 --> 00:35:08.847
We came here so you can meet
your friends.

00:35:10.177 --> 00:35:10.905
Hmm.

00:35:11.834 --> 00:35:12.654
Hey, Krit.

00:35:12.854 --> 00:35:15.568
If you want to call a host over,
I'm totally fine with it.

00:35:17.207 --> 00:35:19.174
Why would I call one, huh?

00:35:21.870 --> 00:35:23.728
I already have one right here.

00:35:25.003 --> 00:35:30.704
Well...

00:35:30.704 --> 00:35:32.016
Couples these days

00:35:32.016 --> 00:35:34.525
even come to host bars together?

00:35:34.984 --> 00:35:37.061
This is an exception, Foei.

00:35:37.589 --> 00:35:39.665
My boyfriend brought me
here to celebrate.

00:35:40.103 --> 00:35:41.302
Well,

00:35:41.302 --> 00:35:43.706
I've already graduated.
Just need to get my diploma.

00:35:43.706 --> 00:35:48.463
Hey, then we must celebrate.

00:35:48.463 --> 00:35:51.778
Whoa! Wait!

00:35:52.178 --> 00:35:55.220
How can you celebrate without us?

00:35:55.220 --> 00:35:57.133
Yeah, come on in!

00:35:57.297 --> 00:35:59.446
- Come on, glasses!
- Here we go!

00:35:59.573 --> 00:36:02.324
Wow, that popped loud!

00:36:02.324 --> 00:36:07.223
- Here you go. Congrats, dear.
- Thank you, Foei.

00:36:07.223 --> 00:36:10.957
- For you, Officer.
- Are you docking our pay for this?

00:36:10.957 --> 00:36:12.487
Oh, yeah, totally.

00:36:12.487 --> 00:36:14.618
I'm even charging you guys
for the water and ice!

00:36:14.618 --> 00:36:18.771
- Whoa.
- You three, be more like your friend.

00:36:18.862 --> 00:36:20.556
Bless!

00:36:20.738 --> 00:36:23.434
Come on. Mm.

00:36:23.434 --> 00:36:25.820
- Come on.
- You guys, bottoms up.

00:36:25.929 --> 00:36:29.991
Let's give Wayu
an informal graduation party!

00:36:37.932 --> 00:36:41.010
- Congratulations, dear.
- Thank you, Foei.

00:36:41.010 --> 00:36:46.056
And you three, why are you
leaving the stage empty?

00:36:46.730 --> 00:36:49.862
Go on, you guys, go!

00:36:50.573 --> 00:36:53.706
Then tonight, Foei, you go up
and perform with us too.

00:36:53.706 --> 00:36:55.273
- Go on, hurry up!
- Me too?

00:36:55.273 --> 00:36:56.656
- Yeah, you too, Foei.
- Wait!

00:36:56.656 --> 00:36:58.441
- Go on!
- Right here, come on.

00:36:58.441 --> 00:37:00.918
- Right here?
- Yeah, Tai.

00:37:03.286 --> 00:37:04.871
Hey!

00:37:07.658 --> 00:37:11.118
Keep it going! Go!

00:37:13.158 --> 00:37:16.802
Hands up if you're not drunk yet!

00:37:17.967 --> 00:37:21.755
- Uh-huh, boom-boom, pow!
- Wayu!

00:37:23.959 --> 00:37:24.834
Mind.

00:37:24.834 --> 00:37:27.786
Quick, hand up!

00:37:27.786 --> 00:37:33.012
Hands up! Come on, woo-hoo!

00:37:46.308 --> 00:37:48.366
How've you been, Mind? You disappeared.

00:37:49.423 --> 00:37:51.044
I've been working with my family lately.

00:37:51.463 --> 00:37:53.612
Once things got better,
I started going out.

00:37:55.342 --> 00:37:57.510
Wayu, you're graduated now.

00:37:58.056 --> 00:38:00.916
Yeah, I just turned in my final project.

00:38:00.916 --> 00:38:02.591
Just need to get my diploma.

00:38:03.010 --> 00:38:04.194
Congrats in advance!

00:38:04.613 --> 00:38:06.052
- Thanks.
- Mm.

00:38:09.604 --> 00:38:11.316
You don't need to be that protective.

00:38:11.972 --> 00:38:12.955
I've got a partner now.

00:38:14.886 --> 00:38:16.853
- Really?
- Really.

00:38:17.600 --> 00:38:18.638
We just started dating.

00:38:19.039 --> 00:38:20.787
Well, he was supposed to come today.

00:38:20.787 --> 00:38:22.754
But he's busy with work,
so he couldn't make it.

00:38:23.028 --> 00:38:24.303
Let's meet another day.

00:38:24.303 --> 00:38:26.379
Sure, just pick a day, Mind.

00:38:29.239 --> 00:38:30.878
Take good care of Wayu.

00:38:31.461 --> 00:38:32.809
He's really serious about you.

00:38:39.584 --> 00:38:40.586
Of course.

00:38:42.608 --> 00:38:44.247
See you again at our wedding!

00:38:44.739 --> 00:38:46.050
I'll send you an invitation.

00:38:48.655 --> 00:38:50.640
Yeah, I'll definitely be there.

00:38:51.679 --> 00:38:52.643
Come on.

00:38:56.869 --> 00:38:57.653
See you.

00:38:59.146 --> 00:39:01.241
- Mm, see you, Mind.
- See you.

00:39:07.962 --> 00:39:08.872
Why?

00:39:16.176 --> 00:39:17.251
Top me up, quick!

00:39:18.635 --> 00:39:20.839
Okay, look here. 3, 2, 1.

00:39:20.842 --> 00:39:22.205
One more. 3, 2, 1.

00:39:22.259 --> 00:39:23.297
Say 'yay' now. 3, 2, 1.

00:39:23.297 --> 00:39:25.192
- Yay!
